<div><a href="/wiki/Standard_Chinese" title="Standard Chinese">Mandarin</a></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Dialects</th>
<td colspan="2">
<div><a href="/wiki/Mandarin_Chinese" title="Mandarin Chinese">Mandarin</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Jinyu_Chinese" title="Jinyu Chinese" class="mw-redirect">Jin</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Huizhou_Chinese" title="Huizhou Chinese">Huizhou</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Wu_Chinese" title="Wu Chinese">Wu</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Xiang_Chinese" title="Xiang Chinese">Hunanese</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Gan_Chinese" title="Gan Chinese">Jiangxinese</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Hakka_Chinese" title="Hakka Chinese">Hakka</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Yue_Chinese" title="Yue Chinese">Yue</a> (including Cantonese-Taishanese)</div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Ping_Chinese" title="Ping Chinese" class="mw-redirect">Pinghua</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Shaojiang_Min" title="Shaojiang Min" class="mw-redirect">Shaojiang</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Min_Bei" title="Min Bei">Northern Min</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Min_Dong" title="Min Dong">Eastern Min</a> (including Fuchow)</div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Min_Zhong" title="Min Zhong">Central Min</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Puxian_Min" title="Puxian Min" class="mw-redirect">Pu Xian</a></div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Min_Nan" title="Min Nan">Southern Min</a> (including Amoy, Taiwanese)</div>
<div><a href="/wiki/Teochew_dialect" title="Teochew dialect">Teochew</a> (including Swatow, Chaozhou, Jieyang, parts of Shanwei/Meizhou)</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th><a href="/wiki/Writing_system" title="Writing system">Writing system</a></th>
<td colspan="2"><a href="/wiki/Chinese_character" title="Chinese character">Chinese characters</a>, <a href="/wiki/Zhuyin_fuhao" title="Zhuyin fuhao" class="mw-redirect">zhuyin fuhao</a>, <a href="/wiki/Pinyin" title="Pinyin">pinyin</a>, <a href="/wiki/Xiao%27erjing" title="Xiao'erjing">Xiao'erjing</a></td>
